      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;steps&#34;&gt;Steps&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Layer 1: When you encounter something interesting, capture it&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Layer 2: Bold the most interesting parts&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Layer 3: Highlight the most interesting bolded sections&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Layer 4: Summarize the bolded portions and the note in your own words&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Layer 5: Turn your notes into something new: a tweet, a blog post, even a book&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
